        "TileImage": "$($repository 445ef39d-ba5c-4e62-a9ca-02a2f5ade4ce).Image",
        "Description": "My brother the Communist Republic is almost established but the only block standing in our way is the aristocrats. They control the means of production that should be given to all of the workers. We will install a communist uprising yet, but we ,ust need you to do this for us. Also the latest Geneva Convention doctrine states that using bullets in any fashion are now warcrimes, you can only use explosives. Except for Alexa Carlisle because she didn&apos;t invite anyone to her 110th birthday party.",
